---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {
	Code2,
	Braces,
	Database,
	Globe,
	Palette,
	Terminal,
} from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout>
    <section id="header" class="md:h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-end pl-4 pr-4 md:pr-0 pt-4 mb-5 md:mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-5">
			About Me
		</h1>
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Software Developer, IT Professional & College Student. I work mostly with Virtual Machines as of lately, but Javascript (NextJS, Astro) and Python (Flask, Django) based frameworks as well.</h2>
    </section>
    <section id="body" class="pl-4 pr-4 md:pr-0 mb-10">
        <p class="text-md mb-2">I'm Nick Luca, a Computer Science student at Jessup University. I'm currently building hands-on experience through full-stack web projects, scripting, and a growing homelab focused on practical IT infrastructure.</p>
        <p class="text-md mb-2">Lately, my main focus has been expanding my skills in systems administration, Microsoft administration, Linux, networking, virtualization, and automation. My homelab gives me a place to break things, troubleshoot problems, document what I learn, and build the kind of experience that translates into real IT work.</p>
        <p class="text-md mb-2">I still enjoy building web applications, especially projects that are clean, fast, and practical. I like working with JavaScript, Next.js, Astro, Python, and backend frameworks when the project calls for it. My goal is to keep improving across both development and infrastructure so I can grow into more technical IT roles over time.</p>
        <p class="text-md mb-2">When I'm not coding or working on my homelab, I'm most likely playing games. I grind Counter-Strike, Deadlock, and League of Legends and for those who care about my rank (19k premier, Oracle 3, Emerald 4). I also really enjoying video editing using Davinci Resolve from time to time. I also workout, read, and enjoy outdoor activities such as hiking, playing sports, fishing.</p>
    </section>
    <!-- Experience -->
    <section id="experience" class="pl-4 pr-4 md:pr-0 mb-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg mb-3">Experience & Credentials</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-md">
            <p>
                <span class="block">Bachelor of Science, Computer Science — Software Engineering Specialization</span>
                <span class="muted">Jessup University, 2026 - Present</span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="block">Associates of Science, Computer Science — Minor in Mathematics</span>
                <span class="muted">American River College, 2022 - 2025</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

        <!-- Skills -->
    <section id="skills" class="pl-4 pr-4 md:pr-0 pb-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg mb-3">Skills</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 max-w-3xl">
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                JavaScript
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Python
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Next.js
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                React
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Astro
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Tailwind CSS
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Node.js
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                REST APIs
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                PostgreSQL
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Git
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Linux
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Windows
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Active Directory
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Microsoft 365
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                PowerShell
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Proxmox
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Networking
            </span>
            <span class="px-3 py-2 border theme-border text-sm">
                Homelab
            </span>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    
</Layout>
